=== Docking Station ===
Surface 3发布后微软也发布了它的拓展坞。其上面拥有2个[[USB_3.0|USB 3.0]]，2个[[USB_2.0|USB 2.0]]，一个千兆以太网接口，一个额外[[Mini_DisplayPort|Mini DisplayPort]]接口，一组[[Phone_connector_(audio)#Computer_sound|3.5]]毫米声音输入输出接口和Surface Pen的放置处。<ref>{{cite web|title=New Surface 3 Docking Station Features 4 USB Ports, Storage for Surface Pen, Mini DisplayPort And More|url=http://microsoft-news.com/new-surface-3-docking-station-features-4-usb-ports-storage-for-surface-pen-mini-displayport-and-more/|website=Microsoft-News.com|accessdate=6 April 2015|date=31 March 2015|archive-date=2015-05-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150521191704/http://microsoft-news.com/new-surface-3-docking-station-features-4-usb-ports-storage-for-surface-pen-mini-displayport-and-more/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

Surface 3还可以连接多种[[USB|USB]]设备和[[蓝牙|蓝牙]]设备，如无线鼠标键盘。

== 评价 ==
Surface 3获得了业界的广泛好评。批评家们认为微软选择从[[ARM_architecture|ARM]]平台转向[[x86|x86]]是个明智的选择。而批评主要集中在相对较短的电池使用时间。<ref name="AT_r">{{cite web|last1=Howse|first1=Brett|title=The Surface 3 Review|url=http://www.anandtech.com/show/9219/the-surface-3-review|website=AnadTech.com|accessdate=8 June 2015|date=4 May 2015|archive-date=2015-06-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150609193704/http://anandtech.com/show/9219/the-surface-3-review|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="E_r">{{cite web|last1=Hardawar|first1=Devindra|title=Surface 3 review: Finally, a cheap Surface you'd actually want|url=http://www.engadget.com/2015/04/15/surface-3-review/|website=Engadget.com|accessdate=8 June 2015|date=15 April 2015|archive-date=2015-06-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150616165114/http://www.engadget.com/2015/04/15/surface-3-review/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="DT_r">{{cite web|last1=Smith|first1=Matt|title=The new Surface 3 runs full-blown Windows 8.1 just like its Pro sibling|url=http://www.digitaltrends.com/computing/microsoft-surface-3-review/|website=DigitalTrends.com|accessdate=8 June 2015|archive-date=2015-06-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150607140127/http://www.digitaltrends.com/computing/microsoft-surface-3-review/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

